title: Phraparit Mō̜n sipsō̜ng tamnān phrō̜mthang ʻatthakathā læ ʼathibāi
other_titles: Sala patʻ paruitʻ Manʻ cahʻ bā khanʻ mvai hānʻ koumʹ Pāḷi ʼaratha ʼadhipāai mūla drapʻ Kyāʻ janoʻ Paduma Bhāpranʻ
Phrakhamphī phraparit Mō̜n sipsō̜ng tamnān phrō̜mthang Bālī, khamplǣ yoksap, læ plǣ dōi ʻat tōn chabap Phra ʻathikān Bunnāk Pathumō

description.value: On Buddhist scripture of Phraparit protective chants of Mon ; volume commemoration of 40th anniversary of Thai Raman Association.

notes.value:
